{"id": 61098, "date": "2025-10-10T04:00:12", "date_gmt": "2025-10-10T11:00:12", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=61098"}, "modified": "2026-06-11T13:08:55", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-11T20:08:55", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-october-10-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/10/kingdom-of-days-october-10-2/", "title": {"rendered": "October 10"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays at Grendel\u2019s Lair Coffee House in Philadelphia.</p>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play a Lawsuit Tour show at Miami University in Oxford, Ohio. Based on the student newspaper clipping below, it seems that Bruce&#8217;s shows are not necessarily easy to book or facilitate due to Bruce&#8217;s legal battle with Mike Appel. At one point, the school seemed unsure about whether this concert would happen.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-61098-6\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08-Growin-Up.mp3?_=6\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08-Growin-Up.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08-Growin-Up.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4744\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-1010/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1010.jpg?fit=421%2C576&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"421,576\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-1010\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1010.jpg?fit=421%2C576&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4744 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1010.jpg?resize=421%2C576&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"421\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1010.jpg?w=421&amp;ssl=1 421w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1010.jpg?resize=219%2C300&amp;ssl=1 219w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 421px) 100vw, 421px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1980:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the River Tour to Chicago for the first of two nights at the Uptown Theater, where they tour premiere a show-closing &#8220;Raise Your Hand.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-OALtiJWP-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/OALtiJWP?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21724\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1980-10-10-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1980-10-10.jpg?fit=2423%2C1382&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2423,1382\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quo